snippet.title: Announcing PROMOD // DEV VLOG #001
snippet.description:
FAST PACED // TACTICAL // SHOOTER
Lock & load into the neo modern warfare simulation of PROMOD – The only 5v5 fast paced alternative to modern tactical FPS, requiring fluid movement and unparalleled precision, with every skirmish on the knife edge of altering the rules of modern warfare.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1442170/?utm_source=YouTube/?utm_campaign=PMD

Get involved and join our official Discord to give your input on early development.
Discord: https://discord.gg/GYEEKFhPcP

SOCIAL //
Facebook: www.facebook.com/PlayPromod 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayPromod 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playpromod/

https://playpromod.gg/community-commitment
